---
title: Smokey Beef & Garlic Rice Bowl with Roasted Rainbow Veggies & Sour Cream
description: When you can't get no satisfaction, you need a hearty beef bowl just like this! With a rich tomato sauce flavoured with our
Louisiana spice blend, plus tender roasted veggies and charred corn, it's truly got the lot.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/american-beef-bowl-spiced-corn-cobs-b8fc5578.jpg
